# Styling Rules

## Tailwind CSS Guidelines
- Use Tailwind utility classes exclusively - no custom CSS unless absolutely necessary
- Follow mobile-first responsive design: `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:` breakpoints
- Use semantic color names from `tailwind.config.js`: `primary-*`, `gray-*`, `dark-*`
- Apply consistent spacing using Tailwind's spacing scale: `p-4`, `m-8`, `space-y-6`

## Typography Standards
- Use Barlow font for all headings and subheadings: `font-barlow`
- Main headings use bold weight: `font-bold` (700)
- Subheadings use regular weight: `font-normal` (400)
- Apply custom font sizes: `text-heading-1` through `text-heading-6`, `text-body-large`
- Note: `text-heading-6` uses light weight (300) to match body text consistency
- Use `leading-relaxed` for body text readability
- Body text uses Work Sans (default sans-serif)
- Logo uses `.logo` class with Barlow bold (700) and `!important` declaration

## Color Palette
- Main brand color: `brand-4` (#006DE0) for header and services section
- Brand color variations: `brand-1` through `brand-5` for different UI elements
- Custom grays: `custom-gray-light`, `custom-gray-medium`, `custom-gray-dark`, `custom-gray-darker`
- Custom blues: `custom-blue-light`, `custom-blue-medium`, `custom-blue-dark`, `custom-blue-brand`, `custom-blue-navy`
- Text hierarchy: `text-gray-950` (dark), `text-gray-600` (medium), `text-white` (light backgrounds)
- Backgrounds: `bg-gray-50` (light), `bg-gray-800` (dark sections), `bg-brand-4` (main brand)
- Interactive states: `hover:text-gray-200`, `hover:bg-brand-5`

## Layout Patterns
- Use `container mx-auto px-4` for consistent page width and padding
- Apply `max-w-*` constraints: `max-w-4xl`, `max-w-2xl` for content sections
- Use flexbox utilities: `flex`, `items-center`, `justify-between` for alignment
- Apply consistent section spacing: `py-20` for major sections, `py-8` for smaller
- Mobile burger menu button: `w-15 h-15` (60px) with `p-4` padding for accessibility

## Accessibility Requirements
- Ensure minimum 4.5:1 color contrast ratio for text
- Main brand color (#006DE0) provides excellent accessibility rating
- Use `sr-only` class for screen reader only content
- Apply `focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500` for focus indicators
- Include `aria-label` attributes for interactive elements without visible text
- Mobile touch targets minimum 60px (w-15 h-15) for burger menu

## Performance Considerations
- Use `antialiased` class on body for better font rendering
- Apply `transition-colors` for smooth hover effects
- Optimize images with appropriate `object-cover` and sizing
- Use CSS custom properties sparingly - prefer Tailwind utilities
- Google Fonts loaded with `display=swap` for optimal performance
- Font preconnect links in HTML head for faster font loading